latestPosts.caption: it didn’t go how we planned but God is good and baby boy is healthy and that’s all that matters🩵

Our mighty little miracle🩵 

Eziah Blue 
Ez-eye-uh 
6/26/25
9lbs, 21 in

The best thing that’s ever happened to us! Feels like we’ve known him our whole lives.

After 2 days of active labor, hours of pushing, we were rushed into an emergency C-section due to baby boys heart rate dropping. The hardest and most painful few days ended with the most beautiful blessing from God. Life is so precious and we will never take for granted the miracle it is. So grateful for our community of people surrounding us with love and prayer during this time! It really does take a village
